Questions:
Are you thirsty? => Sania’táthens ken
Are you hungry? => Satonhkária’ks ken
Are you hot? => Sa’tarihà:se ken
Are you cold? => Sewístohs ken
Do you need to call your family? => Tesatonhontsó:ni ken iasheiatewennátaahse ne sahwá:tsire
Do you need to go to the bathroom? => Tesatonhontsó:ni ken átste ieienhtáhkhwa iáhse  

Statements:
I am thirsty. => Wakenia’táthens
I am hungry. => Katonhkária’ks
I am hot. => Waka’tarihà:se
I am cold. => Kewístohs
I need to call my family. => Tewakatonhontsó:ni iakheiatewennátaahse ne akhwá:tsire
I need to go to the bathroom. => Tewakatonhontsó:ni átste ieienhtáhkhwa iá:ke 
